WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.840
There are times that you may want to export your work from RStudio Cloud, and we've done

00:00:07.840 --> 00:00:11.280
our best to make it as easy as possible for you.

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:15.840
Navigating to our workspace from within RStudio Cloud, we see that there are a few projects

00:00:15.840 --> 00:00:17.020
listed.

00:00:17.020 --> 00:00:22.320
To the right of each project is an export button, and by clicking on this, RStudio Cloud

00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:26.280
initiates the creation of a project file that we can download.

00:00:26.280 --> 00:00:30.320
Once complete, the pop-up shows us a download button.

00:00:30.320 --> 00:00:34.680
Clicking the download button downloads a zip file with all of the associated project files

00:00:34.680 --> 00:00:36.639
that we can now run on our local machine.

